Staking b% differences method 1

If the bref cannot be estimated, the 150 events closest to the hypocenter are considered. The bref is assumed constant for the entire period of the PRE catalog.

Index

Staking b% differences method 2

If the bref cannot be estimated using the time series, the 150 events closest to the hypocenter are considered. The bref is considered valid only for the day -1 (1 day before the mainshock occurrence).
